# <div style="text-align: center;">利基模高斯光束、厄米-高斯光束和拉盖尔-高斯光束真空中任意传播距离z处的电场</div>

## 一、数学准备

1.规定源平面变量：

{% katex %}
\xi=\rho\cos{\phi},\eta=\rho\sin{\phi}.
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

2.规定参考平面变量：

{% katex %}
x=r\cos{\varphi},y=r\sin{\varphi}.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

3.菲涅耳衍射公式：

{% katex %}
U_o (x,y )=\frac{exp (jkz )}{j\lambda z}\iint_{-\infty}^{\infty}{U_i (\xi,\eta )}exp \{\frac{jk}{2z} [ (\xi-x )^2+ (\eta-y )^2 ] \}d\xi d\eta,
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
U_o (r,\varphi )=\frac{exp (jkz )}{j\lambda z}\int_{0}^{2\pi}\int_{0}^{\infty}{U_i (\rho,\phi )}exp \{\frac{jk}{2z} [\rho^2+r^2-2\rho r\cos{ (\phi-\varphi )} ] \}\rho d\rho d\phi.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

4.高斯光束参数：

{% katex %}
z_0=\frac{\pi W_0^2}{\lambda}=\frac{1}{2}kW_0^2,
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
W(z)=W_0^2[1+(\frac{\lambda z}{\pi W_0^2})]^2=W_0(1+\frac{z^2}{z_0^2})^\frac{1}{2},
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
R(z)=z(1+\frac{z_0^2}{z^2})=\frac{z_0^2+z^2}{z}.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

5.必要的积分公式：

{% katex %}
\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}exp(-ax^2)dx=(\frac{\pi}{a})^\frac{1}{2},
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}{exp[-\frac{(x-y)^2}{2u}]H_m(x)dx}=(2\pi u)^\frac{1}{2}(1-2u)^\frac{m}{2}H_m[y(1-2u)^{-\frac{1}{2}}],0\le u\le\frac{1}{2},
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
\int_{0}^{2\pi}exp[-jx\cos{(\varphi_1-\varphi_2)}+jl\varphi_1]d\varphi_1
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\sum_{-\infty}^{\infty}{\int_{0}^{2\pi}(-j)^mJ_m(x)exp[jm(\varphi_1-\varphi_2)]exp(jl\varphi_1)d\varphi_1}
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=2\pi(-j)^lJ_l(x)exp(jl\varphi_2).
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
\int_{0}^{\infty}x^{l+1}exp[-\beta x^2]L_p^l(\alpha x^2)J_l(xy)dx=2^{-l-1}\beta^{-l-p-1}(\beta-\alpha)^py^lexp(-\frac{y^2}{4\beta})L_p^l[\frac{y^2}{4\beta(\alpha-\beta)}].
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

6.一个重要定义：

{% katex %}
1+j\frac{z}{z_0}=Rexp[j\phi(z)].
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

则：

{% katex %}
R=[1+\frac{z^2}{z_0^2}]^\frac{1}{2}=\frac{W(z)}{W_0},\phi(z)=\tan{\frac{z}{z_0}}.
{% endkatex %}

## 二、基模-高斯光束

源平面电场表达式：

{% katex %}
U_i(\xi,\eta)=exp(-\frac{\xi^2+\eta^2}{W_0^2}).
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

代入菲涅耳衍射公式：

{% katex %}
U_o(x,y)=\frac{exp(jkz)}{j\lambda z}\iint_{-\infty}^{\infty}exp(-\frac{\xi^2+\eta^2}{W_0^2})exp\{\frac{jk}{2z}[(\xi-x)^2+(\eta-y)^2]\}d\xi d\eta
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{exp(jkz)}{j\lambda z}\iint_{-\infty}^{\infty}exp[-\frac{\xi^2}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}(\xi-x)^2]exp[-\frac{\eta^2}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}(\eta-y)^2]d\xi d\eta
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{exp(jkz)}{j\lambda z}\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}exp[-\frac{\xi^2}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}(\xi-x)^2]d\xi\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}exp[-\frac{\eta^2}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}(\eta-y)^2]d\eta.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

设：

{% katex %}
A=\frac{exp(jkz)}{j\lambda z},
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
I_x=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}exp[-\frac{\xi^2}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}(\xi-x)^2]d\xi,
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
I_y=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}exp[-\frac{\eta^2}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}(\eta-y)^2]d\eta.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

则有：

{% katex %}
U_o(x,y)=A\cdot I_x\cdot I_y.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

考虑I_x：

{% katex %}
I_x=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}exp[-\frac{\xi^2}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}(\xi-x)^2]d\xi
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}exp[-\frac{\xi^2}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}(\xi^2-2\xi x+x^2)]d\xi\\=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}exp[(-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z})(\xi^2-2\frac{\frac{jk}{2z}}{-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}}\xi x+(\frac{\frac{jk}{2z}}{-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}})^2x^2)+\frac{jk}{2z}x^2-\frac{(\frac{jk}{2z})^2}{-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}}x^2]d\xi
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}exp[(-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z})(\xi-\frac{\frac{jk}{2z}}{-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}}x)^2+\frac{jk}{2z}(1-\frac{\frac{jk}{2z}}{-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}})x^2]d\xi
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=exp[\frac{jk}{2z}\frac{\frac{1}{W_0^2}}{\frac{1}{W_0^2}-\frac{jk}{2z}}x^2]\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}{exp[-(\frac{1}{W_0^2}-\frac{jk}{2z})(\xi-\frac{\frac{jk}{2z}}{-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}}x)^2]d\xi.} 
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

设：

{% katex %}
a=\frac{1}{W_0^2}-\frac{jk}{2z},
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
b=\frac{jk}{2z}\frac{\frac{1}{W_0^2}}{\frac{1}{W_0^2}-\frac{jk}{2z}}x^2=\frac{jk}{2z}\frac{1}{1-\frac{jk}{2z}W_0^2}x^2=\frac{jk}{2z}\frac{1}{1-j\frac{z_0}{z}}x^2=\frac{jk}{2z}\frac{(1+j\frac{z_0}{z})}{(1-j\frac{z_0}{z})(1+j\frac{z_0}{z})}x^2
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{jk}{2z}\frac{(1+j\frac{z_0}{z})}{1+\frac{z_0^2}{z^2}}x^2=\frac{jk}{2}\frac{(z+jz_0)}{z^2+z_0^2}x^2=\frac{jk}{2}\frac{z}{z^2+z_0^2}x^2-\frac{k}{2}\frac{z_0}{z^2+z_0^2}x^2
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{jk}{2R(z)}x^2-\frac{1}{2}\frac{2z_0}{W_0^2}\frac{z_0}{z^2+z_0^2}x^2=\frac{jkx^2}{2R(z)}-\frac{x^2}{W^2(z)},
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
t=\xi-\frac{\frac{jk}{2z}}{-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}}x.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

得：

{% katex %}
I_x=exp(b)\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}exp(-at^2)dt.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

利用积分公式：

{% katex %}
\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}exp(-ax^2)dx=(\frac{\pi}{a})^\frac{1}{2}.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

得：

{% katex %}
I_x=exp(b)(\frac{\pi}{a})^\frac{1}{2}.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

其中：

{% katex %}
\frac{1}{a}=\frac{1}{\frac{1}{W_0^2}-\frac{jk}{2z}}=\frac{1}{\frac{1}{W_0^2}-\frac{j}{2z}\frac{2z_0}{W_0^2}}=\frac{W_0^2}{1-j\frac{z_0}{z}}=j\frac{W_0^2}{j+\frac{z_0}{z}}=j\frac{W_0^2\frac{z}{z_0}}{j\frac{z}{z_0}+1}
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=jW_0^2\frac{z}{z_0}\frac{z_0}{[z_0^2+z^2]^\frac{1}{2}}exp[-j\phi(z)]

{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}=j\frac{2z_0}{k}\frac{z}{z_0}\frac{z_0}{[z_0^2+z^2]^\frac{1}{2}}exp[-j\phi(z)]
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=j\frac{2z}{k}\frac{W_0}{W(z)}exp[-j\phi(z)],
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
[\frac{\pi}{a}]^\frac{1}{2}=[j\pi\frac{2z}{k}\frac{W_0}{W(z)}exp[-j\phi(z)]]^\frac{1}{2}=[j\lambda z\frac{W_0}{W(z)}exp[-j\phi(z)]]^\frac{1}{2}.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

则：

{% katex %}
I_x=exp[\frac{jkx^2}{2R(z)}-\frac{x^2}{W^2(z)}]\cdot[j\lambda z\frac{W_0}{W(z)}exp[-j\phi(z)]]^\frac{1}{2}.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

同理可得：

{% katex %}
I_y=exp[\frac{jky^2}{2R(z)}-\frac{y^2}{W^2(z)}]\cdot[j\lambda z\frac{W_0}{W(z)}exp[-j\phi(z)]]^\frac{1}{2}.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

综上可得：

{% katex %}
U_o(x,y)=A\cdot I_x\cdot I_y
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{exp(jkz)}{j\lambda z}exp[\frac{jkx^2}{2R(z)}-\frac{x^2}{W^2(z)}][j\lambda z\frac{W_0}{W(z)}exp[-j\phi(z)]]^\frac{1}{2}\cdot exp[\frac{jky^2}{2R(z)}-\frac{y^2}{W^2(z)}][j\lambda z\frac{W_0}{W(z)}exp[-j\phi(z)]]^\frac{1}{2}
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{exp(jkz)}{j\lambda z}j\lambda z\frac{W_0}{W(z)}exp[-j\phi(z)]exp[\frac{jk(x^2+y^2)}{2R(z)}-\frac{(x^2+y^2)}{W^2(z)}]
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{W_0}{W(z)}exp[-\frac{r^2}{W^2(z)}]exp\{j(kz-\phi(z)+\frac{kr^2}{2R(z)})\}.
{% endkatex %}

## 三、厄米-高斯光束

源平面电场表达式：

{% katex %}
U_i(\xi,\eta)=H_m(\frac{\sqrt2\xi}{W_0})H_n(\frac{\sqrt2\eta}{W_0})exp(-\frac{\xi^2+\eta^2}{W_0^2}).
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

代入菲涅耳衍射公式：

{% katex %}
U_o(x,y)=\frac{exp(jkz)}{j\lambda z}\iint_{-\infty}^{\infty}{H_m(\frac{\sqrt2\xi}{W_0})H_n(\frac{\sqrt2\eta}{W_0})exp(-\frac{\xi^2+\eta^2}{W_0^2})}\cdot exp\{\frac{jk}{2z}[(\xi-x)^2+(\eta-y)^2]\}d\xi d\eta
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{exp(jkz)}{j\lambda z}\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}{H_m(\frac{\sqrt2\xi}{W_0})exp[-\frac{\xi^2}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}(\xi-x)^2]d\xi}\cdot\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}{H_n(\frac{\sqrt2\eta}{W_0})exp[-\frac{\eta^2}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}(\eta-y)^2]d\eta}.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

设：

{% katex %}
A=\frac{exp(jkz)}{j\lambda z},
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
I_x=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}{H_m(\frac{\sqrt2\xi}{W_0})exp[-\frac{\xi^2}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}(\xi-x)^2]d\xi},
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
I_y=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}{H_n(\frac{\sqrt2\eta}{W_0})exp[-\frac{\eta^2}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}(\eta-y)^2]d\eta}.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

则有：

{% katex %}
U_o(x,y)=A\cdot I_x\cdot I_y.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

考虑I_x：

{% katex %}
I_x=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}{H_m(\frac{\sqrt2\xi}{W_0})exp[-\frac{\xi^2}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}(\xi-x)^2]d\xi}
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}{H_m(\frac{\sqrt2\xi}{W_0})exp[-\frac{\xi^2}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}(\xi^2-2\xi x+x^2)]d\xi}
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}{H_m(\frac{\sqrt2\xi}{W_0})exp[(-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z})(\xi^2-2\frac{\frac{jk}{2z}}{-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}}\xi x+(\frac{\frac{jk}{2z}}{-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}})^2x^2)+\frac{jk}{2z}x^2-\frac{(\frac{jk}{2z})^2}{-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}}x^2]d\xi}
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}{H_m(\frac{\sqrt2\xi}{W_0})exp[(-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z})(\xi-\frac{\frac{jk}{2z}}{-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}}x)^2+\frac{jk}{2z}(1-\frac{\frac{jk}{2z}}{-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}})x^2]d\xi}
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=exp[\frac{jk}{2z}\frac{\frac{1}{W_0^2}}{\frac{1}{W_0^2}-\frac{jk}{2z}}x^2]\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}{H_m(\frac{\sqrt2\xi}{W_0})exp[-(\frac{1}{W_0^2}-\frac{jk}{2z})(\xi-\frac{\frac{jk}{2z}}{-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}}x)^2]d\xi}
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{W_0}{\sqrt2}exp[\frac{jk}{2z}\frac{\frac{1}{W_0^2}}{\frac{1}{W_0^2}-\frac{jk}{2z}}x^2]\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}{H_m(\frac{\sqrt2\xi}{W_0})\cdot e x p[-(\frac{1}{W_0^2}-\frac{jk}{2z})\frac{W_0^2}{2}(\frac{\sqrt2\xi}{W_0}-\frac{\sqrt2}{W_0}\frac{\frac{jk}{2z}}{-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}}x)^2]d\frac{\sqrt2\xi}{W_0}}.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

考虑积分公式：

{% katex %}
\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}{exp[-\frac{(x-y)^2}{2u}]H_m(x)dx}=(2\pi u)^\frac{1}{2}(1-2u)^\frac{m}{2}H_m[y(1-2u)^{-\frac{1}{2}}],0\le u\le\frac{1}{2}.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

设：

{% katex %}
t=\frac{\sqrt2\xi}{W_0},
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
b=\frac{jk}{2z}\frac{\frac{1}{W_0^2}}{\frac{1}{W_0^2}-\frac{jk}{2z}}x^2=\frac{jkx^2}{2R(z)}-\frac{x^2}{W^2(z)},
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
B=\frac{W_0}{\sqrt2}exp(b)=\frac{W_0}{\sqrt2}exp(\frac{jkx^2}{2R(z)}-\frac{x^2}{W^2(z)}),
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
\frac{1}{2u}=(\frac{1}{W_0^2}-\frac{jk}{2z})\frac{W_0^2}{2},
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
u=\frac{1}{(\frac{1}{W_0^2}-\frac{jk}{2z})W_0^2}=\frac{j\frac{z}{z_0}}{1+j\frac{z}{z_0}}=j\frac{z}{z_0}\frac{z_0}{[z_0^2+z^2]^\frac{1}{2}}exp[-j\phi(z)]=j\frac{z}{z_0}\frac{W_0}{W(z)}exp[-j\phi(z)],
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
1-2u=\frac{1-j\frac{z}{z_0}}{1+j\frac{z}{z_0}}=\frac{\frac{W(z)}{W_0}exp[-j\phi(z)]}{\frac{W(z)}{W_0}exp[j\phi(z)]}=exp[-j2\phi(z)],
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
s=\frac{\sqrt2}{W_0}\frac{\frac{jk}{2z}}{-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{jk}{2z}}x=\frac{\sqrt2}{W_0}\frac{\frac{jk}{2z}}{-\frac{1}{W_0^2}+\frac{j}{z}\frac{z_0}{W_0^2}}x=\frac{\sqrt2W_0\frac{k}{2z}}{j+\frac{z_0}{z}}x=\frac{\sqrt2W_0\frac{k}{2z_0}}{j\frac{z}{z_0}+1}x=\frac{\sqrt2W_0\frac{k}{2}\frac{2}{kW_0^2}}{\frac{W(z)}{W_0}exp[j\phi(z)]}x=\frac{\sqrt2x}{W(z)exp[j\phi(z)]},
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
s(1-2u)^{-\frac{1}{2}}=\frac{\sqrt2x}{W(z)exp[j\phi(z)]}exp[j\phi(z)]=\frac{\sqrt2x}{W(z)}.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

则：

{% katex %}
I_x=B\cdot\int_{-\infty}^{\infty}{H_m(t)\cdot e x p[-\frac{1}{2u}(t-s)^2]dt=B\cdot(2\pi u)^\frac{1}{2}(1-2u)^\frac{m}{2}H_m[s(1-2u)^{-\frac{1}{2}}]}
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{W_0}{\sqrt2}exp(\frac{jkx^2}{2R(z)}-\frac{x^2}{W^2(z)})(2\pi u)^\frac{1}{2}[exp[-j2\phi(z)]]^\frac{m}{2}H_m[\frac{\sqrt2x}{W(z)}]
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{W_0}{\sqrt2}exp(\frac{jkx^2}{2R(z)}-\frac{x^2}{W^2(z)})(2\pi u)^\frac{1}{2}exp[-jm\phi(z)]H_m[\frac{\sqrt2x}{W(z)}].
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

同理可得：

{% katex %}
I_y=\frac{W_0}{\sqrt2}exp(\frac{jky^2}{2R(z)}-\frac{y^2}{W^2(z)})(2\pi u)^\frac{1}{2}exp[-jn\phi(z)]H_n[\frac{\sqrt2y}{W(z)}].
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

综上：

{% katex %}
U_o(x,y)=A\cdot I_x\cdot I_y
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{exp(jkz)}{j\lambda z}\cdot\frac{W_0}{\sqrt2}exp(\frac{jkx^2}{2R(z)}-\frac{x^2}{W^2(z)})(2\pi u)^\frac{1}{2}exp[-jm\phi(z)] \cdot H_m[\frac{\sqrt2x}{W(z)}] \\ \cdot\frac{W_0}{\sqrt2}exp(\frac{jky^2}{2R(z)}-\frac{y^2}{W^2(z)})(2\pi u)^\frac{1}{2}exp[-jn\phi(z)]H_n[\frac{\sqrt2y}{W(z)}]
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{exp(jkz)}{j\lambda z}\cdot\frac{W_0^2}{2}exp(\frac{jk(x^2+y^2)}{2R(z)}-\frac{(x^2+y^2)}{W^2(z)})\\ \cdot2\pi j\frac{z}{z_0}\frac{W_0}{W(z)}exp[-j\phi(z)] \cdot exp[-j(m+n)\phi(z)]H_m[\frac{\sqrt2x}{W(z)}]H_n[\frac{\sqrt2y}{W(z)}]
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{W_0}{W(z)}H_m[\frac{\sqrt2x}{W(z)}]H_n[\frac{\sqrt2y}{W(z)}]exp(-\frac{(x^2+y^2)}{W^2(z)}) \cdot exp\{j[kz+\frac{k(x^2+y^2)}{2R(z)}-(m+n)\phi(z)]\}.
{% endkatex %}

## 四、拉盖尔-高斯光束

源平面电场表达式：

{% katex %}
U_i(\rho,\phi)=(\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0})^lL_p^l(\frac{2\rho^2}{W_0^2})exp(-\frac{\rho^2}{W_0^2})exp(jl\phi).
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

代入菲涅耳衍射公式：

{% katex %}
U_o(r,\varphi)=\frac{exp(jkz)}{j\lambda z}\int_{0}^{2\pi}\int_{0}^{\infty}{(\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0})^lL_p^l(\frac{2\rho^2}{W_0^2})exp(-\frac{\rho^2}{W_0^2})exp(jl\phi)} \\ \cdot exp\{\frac{jk}{2z}[\rho^2+r^2-2\rho r\cos{(\phi-\varphi)}]\}\rho d\rho d\phi
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{exp(jkz)}{j\lambda z}exp(\frac{jk}{2z}r^2)\int_{0}^{\infty}{(\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0})^lL_p^l(\frac{2\rho^2}{W_0^2})exp(-\frac{\rho^2}{W_0^2})exp(\frac{jk}{2z}\rho^2)\rho} \\ \cdot\int_{0}^{2\pi}exp\{\frac{jk}{2z}[-2\rho r\cos{(\phi-\varphi)}]+jl\phi\}d\phi d\rho.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

设：

{% katex %}
A=\frac{exp(jkz)}{j\lambda z}exp(\frac{jk}{2z}r^2),
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
I_{r\varphi}=\int_{0}^{\infty}{(\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0})^lL_p^l(\frac{2\rho^2}{W_0^2})exp(-\frac{\rho^2}{W_0^2})exp(\frac{jk}{2z}\rho^2)\rho I_\varphi d\rho}.
{% endkatex %}

<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
zI_\varphi=\int_{0}^{2\pi}exp\{\frac{jk}{2z}[-2\rho r\cos{(\phi-\varphi)}]+jl\phi\}d\phi.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

则：

{% katex %}
U_o(r,\varphi)=AI_{r\varphi}.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

令：

{% katex %}
a=\frac{k}{z}\rho r.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

则：

{% katex %}
I_\varphi=\int_{0}^{2\pi}exp\{-ja\cos{(\phi-\varphi)}+jl\phi\}d\phi.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

考虑积分公式：

{% katex %}
\int_{0}^{2\pi}exp[-jx\cos{(\varphi_1-\varphi_2)}+jl\varphi_1]d\varphi_1
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\sum_{-\infty}^{\infty}{\int_{0}^{2\pi}(-j)^mJ_m(x)exp[jm(\varphi_1-\varphi_2)]exp(jl\varphi_1)d\varphi_1}
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=2\pi(-j)^lJ_l(x)exp(jl\varphi_2).
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

得：

{% katex %}
I_\varphi=2\pi(-j)^lJ_l(\frac{k}{z}\rho r)exp(jl\varphi).
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

此时：

{% katex %}
I_{r\varphi}=\int_{0}^{\infty}{(\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0})^lL_p^l(\frac{2\rho^2}{W_0^2})exp(-\frac{\rho^2}{W_0^2})exp(\frac{jk}{2z}\rho^2)\rho I_\varphi d\rho}
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=\int_{0}^{\infty}{(\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0})^lL_p^l(\frac{2\rho^2}{W_0^2})exp(-\frac{\rho^2}{W_0^2})exp(\frac{jk}{2z}r^2)2\pi(-j)^lJ_l(\frac{k}{z}\rho r)exp(jl\varphi)\rho d\rho}
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=exp(jl\varphi)2\pi\int_{0}^{\infty}{(-j\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0})^lL_p^l(\frac{2\rho^2}{W_0^2})exp(-\frac{\rho^2}{W_0^2})exp(\frac{jk}{2z}\rho^2)J_l(\frac{k}{z}\rho r)\rho d\rho}
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
=exp(jl\varphi)2\pi\int_{0}^{\infty}{(-1)^l(j\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0})}^lL_p^l[-(j\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0})^2]exp[\frac{1}{2}(j\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0})^2]
{% endkatex %}

<br>

{% katex %}
\cdot exp[-\frac{jk}{2z}\frac{W_0^2}{2}(j\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0})^2]J_l(\frac{k}{z}r\frac{W_0}{j\sqrt2}\cdot j\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0})\frac{W_0}{j\sqrt2}j\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0}\frac{W_0}{j\sqrt2}dj\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0}\\ =-exp(jl\varphi)2\pi\frac{W_0^2}{2}(-1)^l\int_{0}^{\infty}(j\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0})^{l+1}exp[-(-\frac{1}{2}+\frac{jk}{2z}\frac{W_0^2}{2})(j\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0})^2]\\ \cdot L_p^l[-(j\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0})^2]J_l(\frac{k}{z}r\frac{W_0}{j\sqrt2}\cdot j\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0})dj\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0}.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

考虑积分公式：

{% katex %}
\int_{0}^{\infty}x^{l+1}exp[-\beta x^2]L_p^l(\alpha x^2)J_l(xy)dx=2^{-l-1}\beta^{-l-p-1}(\beta-\alpha)^py^lexp(-\frac{y^2}{4\beta})L_p^l[\frac{y^2}{4\beta(\alpha-\beta)}].
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

令：

{% katex %}
B=-exp(jl\varphi)2\pi\frac{W_0^2}{2}(-1)^l,
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
t=j\frac{\sqrt2\rho}{W_0},
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
\alpha=-1,
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
\beta=-\frac{1}{2}+\frac{jk}{2z}\frac{W_0^2}{2}=-\frac{1}{2}+j\frac{z_0}{2z}=-\frac{j}{2}\frac{z_0}{z}(1+j\frac{z}{z_0})
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=-\frac{j}{2}\frac{z_0}{z}Rexp[j\phi(z)]=-\frac{j}{2}\frac{z_0}{z}\frac{W(z)}{W_0}exp[j\phi(z)],
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
s=\frac{k}{z}r\frac{W_0}{j\sqrt2}=\frac{1}{z}\frac{2z_0}{W_0^2}r\frac{W_0}{j\sqrt2}=\frac{z_0\sqrt2}{jzW_0}r.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

则：

{% katex %}
\beta^{-l-p-1}=[-\frac{j}{2} \frac{z_0}{z}\frac{W(z)}{W_0}]^{-l-p-1}\cdot exp[-j(l+p+1)\phi(z)],
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
\beta-\alpha=-\frac{1}{2}+j\frac{z_0}{2z}+1=\frac{1}{2}+j\frac{z_0}{2z}
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{1}{2}(1+j\frac{z_0}{z})=\frac{1}{2}(1+\frac{z_0^2}{z^2})(1-j\frac{z_0}{z})^{-1}
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{1}{2}(1+\frac{z_0^2}{z^2})j\frac{z}{z_0}(1+j\frac{z}{z_0})^{-1}=\frac{j}{2z}\frac{ {z^2+z}_0^2}{z_0}\frac{W_0}{W(z)}exp[-j\phi(z)]
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{ {jz}_0}{2z}\frac{W^2(z)}{W_0^2}\frac{W_0}{W(z)}exp[-j\phi(z)]
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{ {jz}_0}{2z}\frac{W(z)}{W_0}exp[-j\phi(z)],
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
(\beta-\alpha)^p=[\frac{ {jz}_0}{2z}\frac{W(z)}{W_0}]^pexp[-jp\phi(z)],
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
-\frac{s^2}{4\beta}=-(\frac{z_0\sqrt2}{jzW_0}r)^2\cdot\frac{1}{4}\cdot(-\frac{1}{2}+j\frac{z_0}{2z})^{-1}=\frac{z_0^2}{z^2W_0^2}r^2\cdot(-1+j\frac{z_0}{z})^{-1}
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{z_0^2}{z^2W_0^2}r^2\cdot\frac{-1-j\frac{z_0}{z}}{1+\frac{z_0^2}{z^2}}=-\frac{z_0^2}{z^2W_0^2}r^2\frac{z^2}{z^2+z_0^2}-\frac{z_0^2}{z^2W_0^2}r^2\frac{z^2}{z^2+z_0^2}j\frac{z_0}{z}
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=-\frac{r^2}{W_0^2}\frac{z_0^2}{z^2+z_0^2}-j\frac{r^2}{W_0^2}\frac{z_0^2}{z^2+z_0^2}\frac{z_0}{z}=-\frac{r^2}{W^2(z)}-j\frac{k}{2z}\frac{z_0^2}{z^2+z_0^2}r^2.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

{% katex %}
\frac{s^2}{4\beta(\alpha-\beta)}=(-s^2)\cdot\frac{1}{4}\cdot\frac{1}{\beta}\cdot(\frac{1}{\beta-\alpha})
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{ {2z}_0^2}{z^2W_0^2}r^2\cdot\frac{1}{4}\cdot\frac{-2}{j}\frac{z}{z_0}\frac{W_0}{W(z)}exp[-j\phi(z)]\cdot\frac{2z}{ {jz}_0}\frac{W_0}{W(z)}exp[j\phi(z)]
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{2r^2}{W^2(z)}.
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

此时：

{% katex %}
I_{r\varphi}=B\cdot\int_{0}^{\infty}{t^{l+1}exp[-\beta t^2]\cdot L_p^l[\alpha t^2]J_l(s\cdot t)dt}\\ =B\cdot2^{-l-1}\beta^{-l-p-1}(\beta-\alpha)^ps^lexp(-\frac{s^2}{4\beta})L_p^l[\frac{s^2}{4\beta(\alpha-\beta)}]
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=-exp(jl\varphi)2\pi\frac{W_0^2}{2}(-1)^l\cdot2^{-l-1}\cdot[\frac{j}{2}\frac{z_0}{z}\frac{W(z)}{W_0}]^{-l-p-1}exp[-j(l+p+1)\phi(z)]
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
\cdot L_p^l(\frac{2r^2}{W^2(z)})\cdot[\frac{ {jz}_0}{2z}\frac{W(z)}{W_0}]^pexp[-jp\phi(z)]\cdot(\frac{z_0\sqrt2}{jzW_0}r)^l\cdot exp[-\frac{r^2}{W^2(z)}-j\frac{k}{2z}\frac{z_0^2}{z^2+z_0^2}r^2]
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=-2\pi\frac{W_0^2}{2}\cdot2^{-1}[\frac{j}{2}\frac{z_0}{z}\frac{W(z)}{W_0}]^{-1}\cdot2^{-l}(-1)^l[\frac{j}{2}\frac{z_0}{z}\frac{W(z)}{W_0}]^{-l}
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
\cdot(\frac{z_0\sqrt2}{jzW_0}r)^l\cdot L_p^l(\frac{2r^2}{W^2(z)})[\frac{j}{2}\frac{z_0}{z}\frac{W(z)}{W_0}]^{-p}[\frac{ {jz}_0}{2z}\frac{W(z)}{W_0}]^p
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
\cdot exp[-\frac{r^2}{W^2(z)}]\cdot exp[-j\frac{k}{2z}\frac{z_0^2}{z^2+z_0^2}r^2]exp(jl\varphi)exp[-j(2p+l+1)\phi(z)]
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=-\lambda\cdot\frac{z}{j}\frac{W_0}{W(z)}\cdot[-\frac{1}{2}\frac{2}{j}\frac{z}{z_0}\frac{W_0}{W(z)}\frac{z_0\sqrt2}{jzW_0}r]^l \cdot L_p^l(\frac{2r^2}{W^2(z)})
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
\cdot[\frac{j}{2}\frac{z_0}{z}\frac{W(z)}{W_0}]^{-p}[\frac{ {jz}_0}{2z}\frac{W(z)}{W_0}]^p\cdot exp[-\frac{r^2}{W^2(z)}]\cdot exp[-j\frac{k}{2z}\frac{z_0^2}{z^2+z_0^2}r^2]
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
\cdot exp(jl\varphi)exp[-j(2p+l+1)\phi(z)]
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=j\lambda z\frac{W_0}{W(z)}\cdot[\frac{\sqrt2}{W(z)}r]^l\cdot L_p^l(\frac{2r^2}{W^2(z)})\cdot exp[-\frac{r^2}{W^2(z)}]
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
\cdot exp[-j\frac{k}{2z}\frac{z_0^2}{z^2+z_0^2}r^2]exp(jl\varphi)exp[-j(2p+l+1)\phi(z)].
{% endkatex %}
<br>
<br>

综上可得：

{% katex %}
U_o(r,\varphi)=AI_{r\varphi}
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{exp(jkz)}{j\lambda z}exp(\frac{jk}{2z}r^2)\cdot j\lambda z\frac{W_0}{W(z)}\cdot[\frac{\sqrt2}{W(z)}r]^l\cdot L_p^l(\frac{2r^2}{W^2(z)})
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
\cdot exp[-\frac{r^2}{W^2(z)}]\cdot exp[-j\frac{k}{2z}\frac{z_0^2}{z^2+z_0^2}r^2]exp(jl\varphi)exp[-j(2p+l+1)\phi(z)]
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{W_0}{W(z)}\cdot[\frac{\sqrt2}{W(z)}r]^l\cdot L_p^l(\frac{2r^2}{W^2(z)})\cdot exp[-\frac{r^2}{W^2(z)}]exp(jl\varphi)
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
\cdot exp(jkz)exp[j(\frac{k}{2z}-\frac{k}{2z}\frac{z_0^2}{z^2+z_0^2})r^2]exp[-j(2p+l+1)\phi(z)]
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{W_0}{W(z)}\cdot[\frac{\sqrt2}{W(z)}r]^l\cdot L_p^l(\frac{2r^2}{W^2(z)})\cdot exp[-\frac{r^2}{W^2(z)}]exp(jl\varphi)
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
\cdot exp(jkz)exp[j\frac{k}{2}(\frac{z}{z^2+z_0^2})r^2]exp[-j(2p+l+1)\phi(z)]
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
=\frac{W_0}{W(z)}\cdot[\frac{\sqrt2}{W(z)}r]^l\cdot L_p^l(\frac{2r^2}{W^2(z)})\cdot exp[-\frac{r^2}{W^2(z)}]exp(jl\varphi)
{% endkatex %}
<br>

{% katex %}
\cdot exp[jkz+j\frac{kr^2}{2R(z)}-j(2p+l+1)\phi(z)].
{% endkatex %}
